《'''富家窮路'''》（{{lang|en|''Schitt's Creek''}}）是一部[[加拿大|加拿大]]電視[[情景喜劇|情景喜劇]]，於2015年1月13日在[[加拿大廣播公司電視|CBC]]上映<ref name=":2">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/eugene-levy-and-catherine-o-hara-are-up-schitt-s-creek-1.2806231 |title=Eugene Levy and Catherine O'Hara are up Schitt's Creek |date=2014-10-21 |website=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |accessdate=2020-12-23 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203182021/https://www.cbc.ca/news/arts/eugene-levy-and-catherine-o-hara-are-up-schitt-s-creek-1.2806231 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。是由{{tsl|en|Dan Levy (Canadian actor)|丹·列维}}和他的父親[[尤金·列维|尤金·列维]]創作的[[加拿大|加拿大]]電視情景喜劇，於 2015年至2020年在CBC電視台播出。它由6個季80集組成。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Levy |first=Dan |date=March 21, 2019 |title=To Our Dear Fans...pic.twitter.com/FIXjD3gbzA |url=https://twitter.com/danjlevy/status/1108745156059123713 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203181956/https://twitter.com/danjlevy/status/1108745156059123713 |archive-date=February 3, 2021 |access-date=March 21, 2019}}[[Wikipedia:SPS|{{sup]]</ref>由Not a Real Company Productions<ref name="playback">{{Cite magazine |last=Cummins |first=Julianna |date=February 11, 2014 |title=SCTV alums Levy and O'Hara to star in CBC comedy |url=http://playbackonline.ca/2014/02/11/sctv-alums-levy-and-ohara-to-star-in-cbc-comedy/ |url-status=live |magazine=[[Playback_(magazine)|Playback]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801100357/https://playbackonline.ca/2014/02/11/sctv-alums-levy-and-ohara-to-star-in-cbc-comedy/ |archive-date=August 1, 2020 |access-date=January 14, 2015}}</ref>和[[加拿大廣播公司電視|CBC]]製作，該系列講述了以前富有的羅斯家族的考驗和磨難。在他們的業務經理挪用了家族企業Rose Video之後，這個家庭失去了財富，並搬到了他們曾經開玩笑購買的小鎮施密特溪（Schitt's Creek）。現在住在汽車旅館的強尼（[[尤金·列维|尤金·列维]]飾）和莫伊拉（[[凯瑟琳·奥哈拉|凯瑟琳·奥哈拉]]飾）——以及他們的成年子女大衛（{{tsl|en|Dan Levy (Canadian actor)|丹·列维}}飾）和艾莉克絲（[[安妮·墨菲|安妮·墨菲]]飾）——必須適應沒有財富的生活。

該系列的構思來自{{tsl|en|Dan Levy (Canadian actor)|丹·列维}}，他想知道美國真人秀電視上經常描繪的富裕家庭如果失去所有的錢會如何反應。他與他的父親[[尤金·列维|尤金·列维]]進一步發展了該系列，然後將該系列推銷給幾個加拿大和美國的網絡。該系列首先賣給了[[加拿大廣播公司電視|CBC]]，並獲得了最終資金，以開始製作並出售給美國的Pop TV 。雖然在前幾季的受歡迎程度有限，但該系列在第三季後在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上的出現被認為是該劇的地位上升，這歸功於“[[Netflix|Netflix]]的衝擊”和動態的社交媒體存在。<ref>{{Cite web |date=September 20, 2020 |title=Schitt's Creek: Everything You Need to Know About the Emmys' Favorite Comedy |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/09/schitts-creek-emmys-when-final-season-netflix |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203182001/https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2020/09/schitts-creek-emmys-when-final-season-netflix |archive-date=February 3, 2021 |access-date=September 21, 2020 |website=www.vanityfair.com}}</ref>

《富家窮路》（Schitt's Creek）獲得了一致好評並獲得了一批狂熱的追隨者，尤其是它的寫作、幽默和表演。該系列獲得了多項榮譽，包括兩項ACTRA獎和 18項加拿大銀幕獎。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Room, Schitt's Creek Dominate Canadian Screen Awards |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/awards-and-festivals/film-awards/room-hyena-road-lead-early-canadian-screen-award-categories/article29204639/ |url-status=live |access-date=December 8, 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203182022/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/awards-and-festivals/film-awards/room-hyena-road-lead-early-canadian-screen-award-categories/article29204639/ |archive-date=February 3, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=February 22, 2020 |title=Winners: The 18th Annual ACTRA Awards in Toronto {{!}} Markets Insider |url=https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/winners-the-18th-annual-actra-awards-in-toronto-1028928909 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203182022/https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/winners-the-18th-annual-actra-awards-in-toronto-1028928909 |archive-date=February 3, 2021 |access-date=March 2, 2020 |website=markets.businessinsider.com}}</ref>這是第一部獲得評論家選擇電視獎最佳喜劇系列提名的加拿大喜劇系列。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Yeo |first=Debra |date=December 13, 2018 |title=Schitt's Creek Becomes First Canadian Comedy Series Nominated for a Critics' Choice Award |url=https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2018/12/13/schitts-creek-becomes-first-canadian-comedy-series-nominated-for-a-critics-choice-award.html |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506120510/https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2018/12/13/schitts-creek-becomes-first-canadian-comedy-series-nominated-for-a-critics-choice-award.html |archive-date=May 6, 2019 |access-date=January 19, 2019 |website=The Star}}</ref>它還獲得了兩項美國演員工會獎，包括[[喜劇|喜劇]]系列劇的傑出表演和總共19項黃金時段[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名，其中兩次獲得了傑出喜劇系列獎。<ref name="hollywoodreporter">{{Cite web |date=July 16, 2019 |title=Pop TV President Celebrates 'Schitt's Creek' Emmy Breakthrough: "Holy S***!" |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/schitts-creek-breaks-first-emmy-nominations-pop-tv-1224564 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716214559/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/schitts-creek-breaks-first-emmy-nominations-pop-tv-1224564 |archive-date=July 16, 2019 |access-date=July 16, 2019 |website=The Hollywood Reporter |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Nominations Announced for the 26th Annual Screen Actors Guild Awards ® {{!}} Screen Actors Guild Awards |url=https://www.sagawards.org/media/news/releases/nominations-announced-26th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212024926/https://www.sagawards.org/media/news/releases/nominations-announced-26th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE |archive-date=December 12, 2019 |access-date=December 11, 2019 |website=www.sagawards.org |language=en}}</ref><ref name="2020emmys">{{Cite news |date=July 28, 2020 |title=Schitt's Creek Lands Major Comedy Emmy Award Nominations |work=CBC |agency=Associated press |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/us-emmy-nominations-1.5664326 |url-status=live |access-date=July 30, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729020251/https://www.cbc.ca/news/entertainment/us-emmy-nominations-1.5664326 |archive-date=July 29, 2020}}</ref>該節目在第六季也是最後一季獲得了15項提名，創下了[[喜劇|喜劇]]系列最後一季的大多數[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名的記錄。由於對LGBTQ+人的刻畫，該系列獲得了GLAAD 媒體獎傑出喜劇系列的三項提名，兩次獲獎。<ref>{{Cite web |date=January 25, 2019 |title=Outstanding Film – Wide Release – GLAAD Media Awards: The Complete List of Nominees |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/glaad-media-awards-complete-list-nominees-2019-1178509/item/outstanding-film-wide-release-1178523 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426002802/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/glaad-media-awards-complete-list-nominees-2019-1178509/item/outstanding-film-wide-release-1178523 |archive-date=April 26, 2019 |access-date=May 25, 2019 |website=The Hollywood Reporter |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=April 8, 2021|title=Disclosure, Schitt's Creek, Sam Smith, Happiest Season, I May Destroy You, CHIKA, Veneno, Star Trek: Discovery, The Boys in the Band, The Not-Too-Late Show with Elmo among award recipients at the 32nd Annual GLAAD Media Awards|url=https://www.glaad.org/blog/32-glaad-media-awards-winners|access-date=September 22, 2021|website=[[GLAAD|GLAAD]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409151631/https://www.glaad.org/blog/32-glaad-media-awards-winners|archive-date=April 9, 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

在第72屆黃金時段[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]頒獎典禮上，該劇的最後一季包攬了所有七大喜劇獎項。這是喜劇或連續劇第一次獲得所有七個獎項；{{tsl|en|Dan Levy (Canadian actor)|丹·列维}}（Dan Levy）特別獲得了喜劇系列的傑出喜劇系列、寫作和導演（他與安德魯·奇維迪諾分享的最後一部）。它為O'Hara、Murphy和Levys創造了贏得所有四個主要表演類別（男主角/女演員和男配角/女演員）的記錄——這是喜劇或戲劇系列的第一次。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Bilefsky |first=Dan |date=September 21, 2020 |title=Canadians Rejoice as 'Schitt's Creek' Sweeps Emmy Awards |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/21/world/canada/schitts-creek-emmys.html |url-status=live |access-date=September 28, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203182032/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/21/world/canada/schitts-creek-emmys.html |archive-date=February 3, 2021}}</ref>同時，該劇創下了單季喜劇系列獲得艾美獎最多的新紀錄，打破了《了不起的麥瑟爾夫人》 2018年的紀錄，以及最後一季喜劇系列獲得的大多數艾美獎提名和勝利。

